{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Go on a grand adventure and explore the world of Lutum, where everything is made of clay! Chunk, the accidental hero, has unwittingly set off the end of the world, and now must do his best to undo the damage done! Unlock abilities, discover vibrant locations, explore dungeons and fight the evil doers who stand in your way.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>ABILITY UPGRADES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As Chunk explores and progresses through his journey, he will unlock new abilities and powers to help him solve puzzles, reach new areas and fight bosses.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219950/extras/Chunk_Gif2.gif?t=1727247935\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>VIBRANT LOCATIONS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br>Explore a Wacky and Vibrant fantasy world made of Clay. Spanning multiple biomes and filled with unique and colourful side quests and adventures!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219950/extras/Chunk_Gif1.gif?t=1727247935\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>DUNGEON RAIDER!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Delve into an Exciting and Unique range of dungeons on your quest to save Lutum and use your acquired abilities to solve puzzles and defeat bosses. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219950/extras/Chest.gif?t=1727247935\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>COLLECT THE POWER</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Chunk can find POWER DISCS all throughout Lutum which grant him additional buffs that will help him on hi